{"tid":514520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Station 現身，計劃在全球供應免費高速 Wi-Fi","createTime":"2017-12-30T16:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T03:30:01.000Z","uid":28366,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f317d30dabfdad52d77a9f5c93121f5e673ff02a","tid":514520,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/235950_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F235950_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d025c7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 自去年底開始便在印度火車站部署免費 Wi-Fi，企圖擴大印度的上網人口，來增加 Google 服務的用戶與廣告收益。而日前這項 Wi-Fi 計劃已經被改名為 Google Station，並打算推廣到世界各地。此外，著名的 Project Loon 計劃也取得重大進展。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Google Station</strong><br />\n到目前為止，這項計劃的實作仍侷限在印度，預計今年底前在印度的 100 間火車站完成建置，並打算在明年繼續推展到其餘的 300 間火車站。儘管沒有說明網速，但 Google 表示速度足以串流 HD 影片，同時允諾會維持免費。外媒指出，在實測時，Google Station 的 Wi-Fi 能達到 40mbps。<br />\n<br />\n由於在印度，Google 其實是和印度鐵路當局和電信業者合作，因此為了推展服務到其他國家，Google 也開始徵求合作夥伴，同時指出地點將不會只侷限在火車站。而由於許多已開發國家的網路基礎建設足夠，甚至不乏 Google 自己推出的服務，例如星巴克門市的免費 Wi-Fi，因此 Google 的優先目標應該仍是中度或低度開發地區。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Project Loon</strong><br />\n至於 Google 的另外一項著名供網計劃 Project Loon 目前也持續進展。Google 在官方網站指出，為了讓熱氣球能正確移動，Google 花上許多時間處理導航工具，以及軟體演算法，而近日這些工作已經取得明顯進展，能大幅延長 Project Loon 的飛行時間到至少 98 天。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 指出，除了導航工具，新的演算法將能自動計算周邊氣流模型來調整海拔高度，讓氣球能自動升降與漂移。如果一時計算不出來，氣球也懂得先想辦法飄往太平洋，再藉由海風重新調整氣流動向，把自己帶回陸上空域，好維持在同一地區持續供應網路的能力。<br />\n<br />\n據 Google 於南美洲長達 14 週的跨國實驗，氣球總共做了 20,000 次自動海拔與氣流分析。這項實驗的內容是從秘魯開始出發到波多黎各，然後再想辦法在當地上空嘗試能待上多久。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2016/09/29/google-station/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2016%2F09%2F29%2Fgoogle-station%2F&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=93415e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2016/09/29/google-station/</a>"},{"pid":"91ca513c8e21930bc76040e367f61a66d42b1488","tid":514520,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a42f61e1f1d205ef90d84da6ea1938003afe00","tid":514520,"uid":32150,"like":59,"dislike":9,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b6a4688b63c8ca01846a9fa4a427f4e738be57","tid":514520,"uid":49392,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"Kingsman<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c2b7a0972710f3d916b9ad9fde218f10266f1a","tid":514520,"uid":13537,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"用咩機用咩OS,個人資料<br />\nGoogle表示: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad3ac0943a584d0b82008d7bb603b642c40e3e8","tid":514520,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73385df75d25b66b248a4a156f93c21e0c6dda6a","tid":514520,"uid":35814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"96b6a4688b63c8ca01846a9fa4a427f4e738be57","tid":514520,"uid":49392,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"Kingsman<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"植入晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b58dba4deb14520db8ff9b829add31daaa474e","tid":514520,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6cca6c6355943e66db6e43cb134b20e57e7675","tid":514520,"uid":3807,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":2,"replyTim